{"tid":1374124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全世界係咪得香港會咁...","createTime":"2019-07-27T17:17:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T17:25:18.000Z","uid":254523,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0b7a99eaf684ad8a11ea0af805b8985abdeb6f97","tid":1374124,"uid":254523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:17:32.000Z","msg":"可以二百萬人上街<br />\n可以有班義士做勇武<br />\n可以有班和理非做後勤<br />\n可以有班銀髮族出黎遊行<br />\n可以有三十萬人唔怕警黑勾結<br />\n但係到左今時今日仲發動唔到大罷工？<br />\n究竟係咪係香港人眼中罷工係難過以上咁多樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75161bba2218d2208e906498f5e68451d9efbe08","tid":1374124,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:21:24.000Z","msg":"搵食係香港人既死穴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且香港冇似樣既工會<br />\n好難成事"},{"pid":"e14a004c3b7cddae356653a26ccfc33eafedfa0f","tid":1374124,"uid":135798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:23:05.000Z","msg":"因為香港人真係好撚鐘意返工"},{"pid":"2898c90c131a19fb9c27131ba7577393f02a410d","tid":1374124,"uid":242805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:23:07.000Z","msg":"要成立工會 要大洗牌"},{"pid":"a0582c2a6cfc3ccef852c32e0f43cc218cab56a5","tid":1374124,"uid":254523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:23:47.000Z","msg":"有個唔危險 唔會流血 而且對政府有實質影響嘅行動唔肯做 <br />\n反而上街遊行做前線會義無反顧咁做 <br />\n有時真係唔知點講香港人 <br />\n話你地係港豬又唔係 話你地已經醒覺又唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb4f9ccc45fc716368c59fa3d1d8ec15cf0c337","tid":1374124,"uid":278712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:24:58.000Z","msg":"1 香港人返工意識太重。<br />\n2 罷工是要宣傳、計劃，我們之前未試過，嘗試下就會成功。"},{"pid":"7073bfa4c473ffe11f2b7922c48ee8a14d5cd943","tid":1374124,"uid":254523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75161bba2218d2208e906498f5e68451d9efbe08","tid":1374124,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20